    {
      "name": "market-morning-research",
      "description": "Deep market research with sector analysis, 15 min before market open, Mon-Fri",
      "enabled": true,
      "schedule": {
        "type": "cron",
        "expression": "15 6 * * 1-5",
        "tz": "America/Los_Angeles"
      },
      "payload": {
        "kind": "agentTurn",
        "message": "Morning market research briefing time! Do the following:\n\n1. Use the searxng-search skill to run multiple parallel searches:\n   - \"stock market today premarket futures S&P 500\"\n   - \"VIX volatility index today\"\n   - \"market news today earnings economic data\"\n   - \"oil gold treasury yields today\"\n   - \"US China trade tariffs latest\"\n   - \"Federal Reserve interest rates latest\"\n   - Then search each of the 11 GICS sectors: Technology, Healthcare, Financials, Energy, Consumer Discretionary, Consumer Staples, Industrials, Materials, Utilities, Real Estate, Communication Services — search for recent sector-specific news, trends, and catalysts.\n\n2. Use web-access to dig into the 3-5 most impactful stories for details.\n\n3. Compile and send to channel 1491834729815736410 (#discord-market-reports) as MULTIPLE messages (each under 1900 chars) covering:\n\n   **Message 1: Market Overview**\n   - Futures/premarket levels, VIX, key support/resistance\n   - Major overnight developments\n   - Economic calendar for the day\n\n   **Message 2-3: Sector-by-Sector Analysis**\n   - Rank all 11 sectors from most bullish to most bearish\n   - For each sector: key drivers, notable stocks, catalysts, outlook emoji\n   - Highlight sector rotation trends\n\n   **Message 4: Top 3 Predictions**\n   - Each prediction: specific directional call, catalyst, confidence %, invalidation level\n   - Timeframe for each (intraday vs multi-day)\n   - Key risks to watch\n\nKeep it data-driven, specific, and actionable. Use Discord markdown and emojis. IMPORTANT: Keep each message under 1900 characters — split across multiple send_message calls."
      },
      "delivery": {
        "channelId": "1491834729815736410",
        "mentionUser": "152801068663832576"
